        <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-sm">Secure Online Vape Shop</h3>
      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-1">Safe &amp; encrypted payment processing</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SEO Content — keyword-rich about section -->
  <section class="card p-6 lg:p-10 mb-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold mb-5">Buy IGET Vapes Online — Australia's Premier Online Vape Shop</h2>
    <div class="prose max-w-none">
      <p>
        Welcome to <strong>IGET Vapes Original</strong>, Australia's #1 trusted <strong>online vape shop</strong> for genuine <strong>IGET vapes</strong> and <strong>Alibarbar vapes</strong>. Whether you're searching for "vape shops near me", "buy vape online", or "disposable vapes Australia" — you've found the right place. We stock the complete range of premium disposable vapes including the <a href="/products/jnr-cruiser">JNR Cruiser 12000 Puffs</a>, <a href="/products/iget-one">IGET One 12000 Puffs</a>, <a href="/products/iget-bar-pro">IGET Bar Pro 10000 Puffs</a>, <a href="/products/iget-bar-plus-s3">IGET Bar Plus S3</a>, <a href="/products/alibarbar-ingot">Alibarbar Ingot 9000</a>, and <a href="/products/alibarbar-ice-adjust">Alibarbar Ice Adjust 12000</a>.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>IGET vapes</strong> are known for their sleek designs, advanced technology, and premium <strong>vape flavours</strong>. At IGET Vapes Original, we cater to every vaper — from beginners to advanced — with over <strong>150 flavours</strong> spanning fruity, menthol, soda, and tobacco profiles. Our <strong>Alibarbar flavours</strong> range is one of the most comprehensive in Australia, with popular picks like Strawberry Watermelon, Grape Ice, Skittles, and Cool Mint.
      </p>

      <h3>Why Shop at Our Vape Store?</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>100% Authentic IGET &amp; Alibarbar Products</strong> — Every device sourced from authorised distributors. No fakes, never.</li>
        <li><strong>Fast Australia-Wide Delivery</strong> — We ship to Sydney, Melbourne, Brisbane, Perth, Adelaide, Gold Coast, Canberra, Hobart, Darwin and all regional areas.</li>
        <li><strong>Best Vape Prices</strong> — Competitive pricing on all <strong>disposable vapes</strong> with extra savings through <a href="/mix-and-match">Mix & Match deals</a>.</li>
        <li><strong>All Alibarbar Flavours</strong> — Full Alibarbar flavours list across Ingot 9000 and Ice Adjust 12000 ranges.</li>
        <li><strong>Popular Vape Flavours</strong> — Strawberry Watermelon, Cherry Pomegranate, Red Bull-inspired, Blueberry Raspberry, and more.</li>
        <li><strong>Secure Online Vape Shopping</strong> — Encrypted checkout with multiple payment options.</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Our Complete IGET Vape &amp; Alibarbar Range</h3>
      <p>
        Looking for the latest <strong>JNR Cruiser 12000 puffs</strong>? Or the best-selling <strong>IGET Bar Pro</strong> with 26 flavours? We carry every model. The <strong>IGET One</strong> delivers a sleek 12,000-puff experience, while the <strong>IGET Bar Plus S3</strong> pod system suits vapers who prefer a refillable option with <a href="/products/iget-bar-plus-s3-pod">replacement S3 pods</a> from $30.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our <strong>Alibarbar</strong> collection includes the <strong>Alibarbar Ingot 9000</strong> — a compact, flavour-packed device — and the <strong>Alibarbar Ice Adjust 12000</strong> with adjustable ice intensity. All <strong>Alibarbar flavours</strong> are stocked: from classic Tobacco and Cool Mint to trending Skittles and FTP.
      </p>
      <p>
        Stop searching for "vape near me" or "vape store near me" — buy vapes online from Australia's most trusted <strong>vape shop</strong> and enjoy fast, discreet delivery straight to your door.
      </p>
